snippet.title: Guitar Hero 5 Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Guitar Hero 5 is the music game that you will be rocking out to in 2010 at the World Cyber Games competitions! Check out the official launch trailer and get ready to strum your way to the gold medal!
